  "@graph": [
    {
      "comment": "Open-access, file-backed Solid server with WebSocket notifications. Pod data is stored under rootFilePath (configured via CLI/env) so it survives container restarts. Content-level privacy is handled at the Interego client-side encryption layer (JWE), not at the ACL layer — CSS access control stays allow-all for the demo; client encrypts before PUT."
    }
  ]
